des:
Ask Alexa to open Mystical Mind Challenge
She will provide a series of mystical items, beings, animals, and more, to sort in different ways. Train your brain the mystical way. Follow Alexa's directions as fast as possible to rack up points. Challenge yourself, stimulate and improve your memory. Have fun.
Charmed in Company LLP is the oldest mystical metaphysical shoppe in NJ. We created this skill to provide imagery that was themed in a mystical way as you sharpen your brain. Check out our other skills under trivia and lifestyle/self improvement.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
